{
  "entries": [
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "むかしむかし、森の近くに",
      "prompt": "[slowly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Once upon a time, near a large forest,",
      "prompt": "[slowly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "きこりのおじさんとおかみさんが住んでいました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "lived a woodcutter and his wife.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ふたりには、3歳の可愛いおんなのこが",
      "prompt": "[tenderly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "They had only one lovely daughter,",
      "prompt": "[tenderly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ひとりだけいましたが、とても貧乏でした。",
      "prompt": "[sadly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "who was three years old, but they were very poor.",
      "prompt": "[sadly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "毎日のパンもなくなりそうで、困っていました。",
      "prompt": "[worriedly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "They were worried they would run out of bread to eat each day.",
      "prompt": "[worriedly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ある朝、おじさんは悲しい気持ちで森へ",
      "prompt": "[sadly, slowly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "One morning, the woodcutter went to the forest with a heavy heart.",
      "prompt": "[sadly, slowly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "仕事に行きました。木を切っていると、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, steadily]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "As he was cutting a tree, suddenly a beautiful woman appeared,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, steadily]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "突然、頭にキラキラ光る星の冠をつけた、",
      "prompt": "[magically, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "wearing a sparkling star crown on her head.",
      "prompt": "[magically, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "美しいおんなの人が現れました。",
      "prompt": "[wonderingly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"I am the Virgin Mary, the mother of Jesus Christ.",
      "prompt": "[reverently, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「わたしは聖母マリア、イエス・キリストの母です。",
      "prompt": "[reverently, calmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Send your child to me. I will take care of her and raise her happily.\"",
      "prompt": "[warmly, reassuringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "あなたが思う、子供を私のところに",
      "prompt": "[gently, invitingly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "つかわしなさい。わたしが預かり、",
      "prompt": "[gently, reassuringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text8_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "幸せに育てましょう。」",
      "prompt": "[warmly, lovingly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじさんは、そのとおりにして、",
      "prompt": "[obediently, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The woodcutter did as he was told and handed his daughter over to the Virgin Mary.",
      "prompt": "[obediently, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこを聖母マリアに渡しました。",
      "prompt": "[sadly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The Virgin Mary took the girl to heaven.",
      "prompt": "[gently, reassuringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "聖母マリアは、おんなのこを天国へ",
      "prompt": "[gently, lovingly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "There, the girl lived happily.",
      "prompt": "[happily, cheerfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "連れていきました。",
      "prompt": "[gently, lovingly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She ate sweet candies, drank delicious milk, wore golden clothes,",
      "prompt": "[happily, joyfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "天国では、おんなのこは幸せに",
      "prompt": "[happily, cheerfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and played with the angels.",
      "prompt": "[joyfully, playfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "暮らせました。",
      "prompt": "[happily, contentedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "甘いお菓子を食べ、美味しいミルクを飲み、",
      "prompt": "[happily, joyfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text8_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "金色（きんいろ）の服を着て、天使たちと遊びました。",
      "prompt": "[happily, joyfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこが14歳になったある日、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, reflectively]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "One day, when the girl turned fourteen,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, reflectively]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "聖母マリアは言いました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, solemnly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "the Virgin Mary said,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, solemnly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「子よ、私は長い旅に出かけます。",
      "prompt": "[solemnly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Child, I am going on a long journey.",
      "prompt": "[solemnly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "だから、あなたに天国の13個の",
      "prompt": "[seriously, carefully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "So I will entrust you with the keys to the thirteen gates of heaven.",
      "prompt": "[seriously, carefully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "扉（と）のかぎを預けましょう。",
      "prompt": "[seriously, carefully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "You may open twelve of the gates,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, with instruction]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "12個の扉は開けてもいいけれど、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, with instruction]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "but you must never open the thirteenth gate.",
      "prompt": "[sternly, warningly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "13番目の扉は、絶対に開けてはいけません。",
      "prompt": "[sternly, warningly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text7_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "There is a small key. If you open it, misfortune will befall you.\"",
      "prompt": "[ominously, gravely]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text8_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "開けると、不幸が訪れます。」",
      "prompt": "[ominously, gravely]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text9_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこは、絶対に開けないと約束しました。",
      "prompt": "[promiseingly, earnestly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text9_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The girl promised she would never open it.",
      "prompt": "[promiseingly, earnestly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "聖母マリアがいなくなったあと、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, after a pause]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "After the Virgin Mary left,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, after a pause]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこは天国の部屋を見て回りました。",
      "prompt": "[curiously, exploring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "the girl looked around the rooms of heaven.",
      "prompt": "[curiously, exploring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "12個の部屋を見て、どの部屋も",
      "prompt": "[amazed, delighted]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She looked at the twelve rooms and felt happy,",
      "prompt": "[amazed, delighted]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "とてもキラキラしていて、幸せな気持ちになりました。",
      "prompt": "[happily, contentedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "as each room was very dazzling.",
      "prompt": "[happily, contentedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、残った13番目の扉が、",
      "prompt": "[hesitantly, curious]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But the remaining thirteenth gate bothered her.",
      "prompt": "[hesitantly, curious]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "気になって仕方ありません。",
      "prompt": "[curiously, persistently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"I'll just peek a little bit.\"",
      "prompt": "[whispering, mischievously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「ほんの少しだけ、覗いてみよう。」",
      "prompt": "[whispering, mischievously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text7_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "she thought.",
      "prompt": "[thinking, internally]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text8_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこはそう思いました。",
      "prompt": "[thinking, internally]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text8_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The angels said, \"No, that would be a sin.\"",
      "prompt": "[warningly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text9_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "天使たちは「だめですよ。それは罪になります。」",
      "prompt": "[warningly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text9_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But the girl did not listen.",
      "prompt": "[disobediently, ignoring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text10_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "と言いましたが、おんなのこは聞きませんでした。",
      "prompt": "[disobediently, ignoring]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "かぎを開けて、扉を少し開けると、",
      "prompt": "[tentatively, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She opened the lock and slightly opened the gate.",
      "prompt": "[tentatively, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "まぶしい光の中に、三つの髪が",
      "prompt": "[amazed, wondrous]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "In the dazzling light, three gods were sitting.",
      "prompt": "[amazed, wondrous]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "座っていました。",
      "prompt": "[amazed, wondrous]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The girl was surprised.",
      "prompt": "[surprised, shocked]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこはびっくりして、",
      "prompt": "[surprised, shocked]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "When she touched the light with her finger,",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, hesitantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "光に指を触れると、指が金色に",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, hesitantly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "her finger turned golden!",
      "prompt": "[shocked, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "なってしまいました！",
      "prompt": "[shocked, fearfully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Frightened, the girl quickly closed the gate and fled.",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, running]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "怖くなって、おんなのこは扉をけして逃げました。",
      "prompt": "[fearfully, running]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "しばらくして、聖母マリアが帰ってきました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, returning]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "After a while, the Virgin Mary returned.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, returning]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「13番目の扉を開けましたか？」",
      "prompt": "[questioningly, seriously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Did you open the thirteenth gate?\" asked the Virgin Mary.",
      "prompt": "[questioningly, seriously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "と聖母マリアは聞きました。",
      "prompt": "[questioningly, seriously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The girl said no, but the Virgin Mary knew she was lying,",
      "prompt": "[discerningly, knowingly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこは、いいえ、とうそを言いました。",
      "prompt": "[lying, nervously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "by touching the girl's pounding heart.",
      "prompt": "[knowing, sensing]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、聖母マリアは、おんなのこ",
      "prompt": "[knowing, sensing]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "And seeing the golden finger, she finally knew the truth.",
      "prompt": "[realizing, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "のドキドキする心臓（こころ）を触って、",
      "prompt": "[realizing, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text6_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"You lied. You are no longer worthy of being in heaven.\"",
      "prompt": "[sternly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text7_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "うそだとわかりました。",
      "prompt": "[realizing, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text8_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そして、金色になった指を見て、",
      "prompt": "[realizing, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text9_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ついに真実を知りました。",
      "prompt": "[realizing, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text10_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「あなたはうそをつきましたね。",
      "prompt": "[sternly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text11_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "もう天国にいる資格はありません。」",
      "prompt": "[sternly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこが目を覚ますと、",
      "prompt": "[waking, confused]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "When the girl woke up, she was in the middle of a wilderness.",
      "prompt": "[waking, confused]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そこは荒野（こうや）の真ん中でした。",
      "prompt": "[disoriented, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She could not utter a sound and was blocked by thorny hedges,",
      "prompt": "[despairingly, trapped]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "声も出せず、いばらの垣根にさえぎられ、",
      "prompt": "[despairingly, trapped]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "unable to escape anywhere.",
      "prompt": "[hopelessly, lost]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "どこにも逃げられません。",
      "prompt": "[hopelessly, lost]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "She lived miserably in a hollow tree,",
      "prompt": "[miserably, lonely]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "木の窪みをすみかに、木のの実や",
      "prompt": "[lonely, surviving]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "eating berries and wild strawberries.",
      "prompt": "[barely surviving, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text6_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "野性のいちごを食べて、寂しく暮らしました。",
      "prompt": "[miserably, lonely]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ある日、その国の王様が森で狩をしていました。",
      "prompt": "[casually, hunting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "One day, the king of that land was hunting in the forest.",
      "prompt": "[casually, hunting]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "王様は、おんなのこ の美しさにびっくりして、",
      "prompt": "[surprised, admiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The king was surprised by the girl's beauty,",
      "prompt": "[surprised, admiringly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お城に連れて帰り、素敵な服を着せました。",
      "prompt": "[kindly, generously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "took her to the castle, and dressed her in beautiful clothes.",
      "prompt": "[kindly, generously]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おんなのこは声を出せませんでしたが、",
      "prompt": "[silently, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The girl could not speak,",
      "prompt": "[silently, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "王様は、おんなのこを心から愛し、",
      "prompt": "[lovingly, deeply]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text5_en",
      "lang": "en",
